DocAttribute.Name: InterferenceSpace
DocAttribute.Documentation: Optional attribute that expresses the interfering space for _IfcSpatialElement_ occurrences.

DocAttribute.Name: InterferenceType
DocAttribute.Documentation: Optional identifier that describes the nature of the interference.

DocAttribute.Name: ImpliedOrder
DocAttribute.Documentation: Logical value indicating if the _RelatingElement_ is considered a source and the _RelatedElement_ a target (giving a formal orientation to the relation). It shall be provided in regards to _InterferenceGeometry_ usage and _InterferenceType_ declaration.

DocWhereRule.Name: NoSelfReference
DocWhereRule.Documentation: The instance of the _RelatingElement_ shall not be the same instance as the _RelatedElement_.
